Introducing the 11th @jewellerysalon.expo 2021, the most luxurious Jewellery Exhibition In the GCC & the Middle East that will be held from the 2 to 6-Nov-2021 Saudi Arabia, Riyad. 
A Gateway for Prime Jewellers to Mingle with Saudi Elites; Over 600 Number of Exhibiting brands from 50 countries. 
Saudi Arabia has the highest concentration of wealthy families in the MENA region, the Jewellery Salon acts as a gateway for international brands to gain the attention of an exclusive Saudi clientele and for the first time Saudi government gave to Jewellery Salon Management the unique opportunity to allow sales on site. If you are in Riyadh from 2 to 6 November 2021 don’t miss the opportunity to visit the @jewellerysalon.expo
